<p><em>*ahem*</em><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-363086-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-363086-1')">1</a></sup></p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/everything">Everything</a><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-363086-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-363086-2')">2</a></sup></p>
</blockquote>
<p>A noun<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-363086-3" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-363086-3')">3</a></sup> being used in this case<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-363086-4" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-363086-4')">4</a></sup> to represent the totality of relevant data<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-363086-5" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-363086-5')">5</a></sup> pertaining to the statement made by Joreth.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/there#Adverb">there</a><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-363086-6" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-363086-6')">6</a></sup></p>
</blockquote>
<p>A <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deixis">deictic</a> adverb requiring contextual understanding of denotation prior to semantic meaning being assigned. Utilizing contextual analysis, the usage of this word is referring to the location<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-363086-7" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-363086-7')">7</a></sup> of the statement referred to by Joreth.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/entirely">entirely</a><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-363086-8" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-363086-8')">8</a></sup></p>
</blockquote>
<p>Referring to a subjective value-judgment by the original author.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/grammatical">grammatically</a><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-363086-9" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-363086-9')">9</a></sup></p>
</blockquote>
<p>An adverb referencing the rules of standard grammar for the English language as implicitly understood by the original author.</p>
<hr />
<p><em><sub>I have to get back to work, so that's all you're getting for now. I might finish my explication later.</sub></em></p>
